description:
This is a 31 minute workout called 'Whole Body Circuit ' from the channel Rina Thomas.
The workout falls under Strength/Calisthenics.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
You'll need Weights and Rower for this workout.
The workout has a The Warrior Workout and The Competitor vibe.
The The Warrior Workout vibe means Unleash your inner beast. Sweat-dripping, heart-pounding, primal energy. This is especially good for Days when you want to destroy stress and feel invincible. The The Competitor vibe means Gamified, leaderboard-driven, full-send energy. This is especially good for Those who need to chase a score or beat their own record..
The technique difficulty is Beginner and Intermediate.
The effort required is Challenging.

Original workout description: Follow Rina through circuits of whole body dumbbell exercises with cardio intervals on Hydrow
